file tools/.cache/hawm0/ -- new, gitignored (already covered by the existing tools/.cache/ rule); portable JDK, Android cmdline-tools, full SDK install (platform-tools/emulator/platforms/system-images), and the hawm0 AVD itself, all real and on disk (5.5G+)
